lead_paragraph: Mercedes look all but certain to wrap up their third straight Formula One constructors' crown in Sunday's Malaysian Grand Prix but the spectre of a rare defeat in last year's race still haunts them.

headline.print_headline: Wary Mercedes Within Reach of Title Triple
headline.main: Wary Mercedes Within Reach of Title Triple
